---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Remediate Labs"
  description="About Siddharth Sukumar and the Remediate Labs project."
>
  <section class="container-prose pt-16 pb-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">About</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none mt-8">
      <p>
        I'm <strong>Siddharth Sukumar</strong>. I build agent systems for production —
        specifically, ones that have to work reliably without a human in the loop on every step.
      </p>

      <p>
        Remediate Labs is the latest version of that work: a multi-agent platform that watches a
        production deployment, catches errors, diagnoses them against the actual codebase, and
        opens fix PRs. It's been the centerpiece of my engineering work for the last several
        months. The blog covers what I've learned shipping it.
      </p>

      <h2>What I'm working on</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>agent-platform</strong> — the system at <a href="https://app.remediatelabs.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">app.remediatelabs.io</a>.
          5 agents, FastAPI, Postgres + pgvector, ECS Fargate.
          <a href="/projects/agent-platform">Architecture deep-dive →</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Writing</strong> — debugging stories and architecture posts on the
          <a href="/blog">blog</a>.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What I look for</h2>
      <p>
        I'm interested in AI Engineer / agent systems roles where the work involves:
        production-grade agent design, retrieval architecture, eval-driven decisions on model and
        prompt changes, and observability for non-deterministic systems.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Email — <a href="mailto:sidreddy88@gmail.com">sidreddy88@gmail.com</a></li>
        <li>GitHub — <a href="https://github.com/sidreddy88" target="_blank" rel="noopener">sidreddy88</a></li>
        <li>Live demo — <a href="https://app.remediatelabs.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">app.remediatelabs.io</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
